# Calculates rate of CO2 production in ul/s in a multiplexed respirometry run with at least one control chamber

R ulCO2/s = sum( C ulCO2/L * F ml/min * 1e-3L/ml * 1min/60s * 1s ) / ( t.endRecording - t.sealed ) = calc.rate

R.corrected = calc.rate(sample) - calc.rate(control)

sample = two vectors, ppmCO2 & flowrate_ml_min for sample
control = two vectors, ppmCO2 & flowrate_ml_min for control (blank chamber)
